{
  "stem": "13600.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 338.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Jews, because they were-- because they were Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Didn't go west, you mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, further towards Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What happened to them?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't have exact reports.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what I heard from Babruysk, from what I heard later, they were put into wooden houses and burned alive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to realize one things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Jews-- even the Jews who were in different categories, the ones who were living not under communist regime were tortured to death.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The ones who were living in Russia were immediately killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Different approach--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These were killed slowly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These one were killed immediately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All perished.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never heard of them any more, anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't believe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know for sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't have anywhere to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as I know, he-- he-- there was an action in Falenica in 19-- in September '42.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were sent to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Last day I had any-- seen any family, close family, in my life, at the ripe age of 18.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My memory is fading.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know that they took us-- the train went further, deep into Russia to city called Tambov.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tambov was central Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Days.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Definitely days.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was start and stop, and collecting more people, you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 173,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the time, but-- there was so much suffering.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 173,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no air, and no water, and no food, so-- was taken.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 173,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, actually, we were so afraid, that we didn't know what to-- what to fear first, and what to suffer first.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- that came later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] From Tambov, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was sent to a city called Magnitogorsk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ural.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ural mountains, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 178,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ural Mountains, on the way to Siberia, before Siberia, yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
